.siteFooterSection, .IRI .siteFooterSection, html.coverPhoto--poster .filmCoverSection__wrapper .filmCoverSection__bg, html:not(.coverPhoto) .filmCoverSection__wrapper .filmCoverSection__bg, .subPageMenu::after
